snippet.title: [Doom 2] Eriguns 2: The Cathedral
snippet.description: A single map playthrough of the Cathedral (also packed with a second map called "The Catacomb") made by Joel Dube, played with Eriguns 2 and Random Deaths & Decoration with Bolognese Gore Mod; also ran with other mods I can't think of to enhance my Doom experience.
